<h1>Research Interest</h1>
<h3>Topics</h3>
<ul>
<li>Time Series -- Estimation and Diagnostic Procedures</li>
<li>Multivariate Analysis -- Estimation and methodology</li>
<li>Mathematical Statistics -- Estimation</li>
</ul>
<h3>Current Projects</h3>
<ul>
<li><i>Modeling the Ecology of Lake Acton</I> with <a href="http://www.units.miamioh.edu/vannilab/">Vanni labs</a></li>
<li><i>Testing for independence between time series</i> with Michael Robbins</li>
<li><i>Multivariate Time Series modeling and diagnostics</i> with Michael Robbins</li>
</ul>

